        "content": "### Read Pending Queue (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `read` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Keep Valid Bookings · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account",
